operation.   I merely wanted to point out to you that closing the window is
functionally  the  same as pressing the @{"Use" LINK GadUse} gadget.  PowerCache will remain
dormant and active, and can be recalled using the @{"Show Window" LINK GadShowWindow} hotkey.


